:44.000Z","msg":"今日定案？"},{"pid":"d7100851da9a3a3d47184802d78022e7ba72f3ed","tid":455552,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"民主黨主席胡志偉就表示，並不贊成趕走記者，會提出反對意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e22da2f4eae2544a7ff3101cc2a6ec4e159d3d3","tid":455552,"uid":61280,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨主席胡志偉就表示，並不贊成趕走記者，會提出反對意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又急住MY香港？？！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5cec2220328a633c14d5717d5cc75b2283688164","tid":455552,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨主席胡志偉就表示，並不贊成趕走記者，會提出反對意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢班柒頭真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbc65371a853f1111008166542a059a14bf66e8","tid":455552,"uid":16970,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨主席胡志偉就表示，並不贊成趕走記者，會提出反對意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq